window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From the best-selling author of <i>The Daughter </i>and <i>White Lies</i> comes an enthralling psychological thriller unlike anything you’ve heard before!</p> <p>Never make a promise you can’t afford to keep....&nbsp;</p> <p>This is a story about Charlotte - a mother and a wife with the perfect job, the perfect life...at least, that’s how it looks from the outside.</p> <p>But behind closed doors, the marriage is breaking, and Charlotte’s husband, Tris, doesn’t even know how much. He has no idea what Charlotte has planned for him, who she has found, why she has hired someone to pretend to be her. But he doesn’t have long to wait to find out....&nbsp;</p>"; 
